I visited there for my mother's dental pain. It was getting unbearable for her from the last couple of days.

After careful evaluation and an X-Ray, Dr. J. Jyothirmai Reddy came to the conclusion that there was some infection beneath a tooth and it was spreading to the bone underneath. She gave us a couple of options for procedures with pros and cons. We went ahead with the recommendation and she followed through the procedure. Her on the spot judgment and procedure expertise helped my mother retain her dental bridge and all the infected pus was drained out with the assistance of an expert. The pain subsided shortly afterward.

Throughout the procedure and followup visits, she and her colleagues (Dr. Deepesh and Dr. Shaista) were extremely friendly. They patiently heard about what the patient had to say and then acted upon with utmost care. And that's all one can expect from ** ********* doctor.

I would definitely recommend their services to everybody
